title: KAMPS PROPANE is seeking a full-time Route Driver and
text:
KAMPS PROPANE is seeking a full-time Route Driver and ad date: 10/14/2015 
is seeking a full-time Route Driver and Service Tech. Must have: Class B Lic; be able to work independently; mechanically minded; & have clean DMV. Good wage and benefits. Apply in person with resume at 18877 Microtronics Way in Sonora, CA. E.O.E.
